Sky City Chosen as Developer for Auckland Convention Centre

-- B y   B e n   S h a r p l e s
-- 
2011-06-12T04:08:18Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-12/sky-city-chosen-as-developer-for-auckland-convention-centre.html
Sky City Entertainment Group Ltd. (SKC) 
has been selected as the preferred developer of the NZ$350
million ($287 million) New Zealand International Convention
Centre in Auckland, Chief Executive Officer Nigel Morrison said
in an e-mailed statement today. About 1,000 people will be
employed during the construction phase, with the venue to be
opened in January 2015, Morrison said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ben Sharples in  Melbourne  at 
 bsharples@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
